   "Author:   jszeto@adobe.com", 
   "Date:     2011-03-01T00:06:13.865106Z", 
   "Log Message:", 
   "-----------", 
   "Percent height TextArea internal scrolling bug fix", 
   "http://bugs.adobe.com/jira/browse/SDK-29664 - soft keyboard covers textarea on device", 
   "There were two problems. First, the TextAreaSkin was not invalidating the caret position on a resize. The fix is to add a resize handler and invalidate the caret position. The second problem was the TextArea skin's Scroller's viewport didn't have the correct dimensions when the scroll snapping code was run. The fix is to call Scroller.validateNow to ensure the Scroller's viewport is the correct size.", 
   "QE notes: none", 
   "Doc notes: none", 
   "Bugs: SDK-29664", 
   "Reviewer: Glenn", 
   "Tests run: checkintests", 
   "Is noteworthy for integration: no", 
   "Modified Paths:", 
