   "Log Message:", 
   "-----------", 
   "TextArea and Scroller interaction bug fixes", 
   "http://bugs.adobe.com/jira/browse/SDK-29577 - TextArea does not autoscroll(cursor disappers) if TA height is specified", 
   "http://bugs.adobe.com/jira/browse/SDK-29572 - TextArea no longer scrolls to the end when calling appendText().", 
   "Restored the logic in TextAreaSkin for the case when the caret was at the end of the text. This ensures we call validateNow to resize the Group before setting the scroll position.", 
   "- Added support for devices that don't support soft keyboard", 
   "Changed caretBoundsEventHandler to always call ensureElementBoundsIsVisible unless we captured a softKeyboard activate event.", 
   "- Fixed caret position auto scroll bug", 
   "Fixed logic to compare the dimensions of the scrollable area and the element instead of comparing the top and bottom bounds.", 
   "QE notes: none", 
   "Doc notes: none", 
   "Bugs: SDK-29577, SDK-29572", 
